'''Happy Negro''' is an ancient [[Something Awful]] meme and, more recently, an ancient [[4chan]] [[/b/]] meme.  But in reality, his [[PowerWord:IRL Name|name]] is <u>Santino Lee</u> from the [[porn]] website [http://www.Bangbus.com www.Bangbus.com].

==Making of a Legend==
One day he was invited by some [[troll]]s to have sex with lusty [[women]] in the back of a VW Microbus. He was so enamored with their [[boob]]s that he made the most classic face in porn [[evar]], perhaps due to an oncoming [[chimpout]].

==Big in /b/==
It didn't take long for the [[masturbation|fap-happy]] /b/tards to locate this pornographic comedy goldmine, and [[at least 100 years ago]], it was photoshopped onto everything from babies to [[Sonic the Hedgehog]]. This enormous flood of images didn't stop until [[moot]] forced /b/tards to.
 
==Happy Negro Makes Gamer-Themed Porn==
Turns out our beloved black person decided to make a porn site geared towards [[Basement_dwellers|gamerfags]]: [http://www.gearsofwhores.com/main.php Gears of Whores]

